These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, hot-chocolate, coffee
4 different pets are kept: snake, bird, pony, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, boat, taxi, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person drinking milk is the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | juice  | coffee | hot-chocolate    | milk       |
| Pet         | bird | horse    | pony      | snake |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | taxi | boat | skateboard        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, cranberry, potato, artichoke
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, security-guard, videographer, manager
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, van, bus, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the manager##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the person eating potato##1
4. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is the photographer##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | potato   | cranberry | lime     | artichoke      |
| Job         | security-guard | videographer | manager | photographer |
| Transport   | van    | snowmobile   | bus     | jet-ski      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, writing, hiking, traveling
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, metal, folk, techno
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, british, french, german
1. the fan of metal is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the british is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is the fan of folk##1
5. the german is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the german is on the right of the french##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | baking | writing | hiking | traveling |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | metal    | house | folk     |
| Nationality   | turkish | french    | german | british    |

