.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, entrepreneur, dressmaker, mechanic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, baseball, golf
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile, boat, van
1. the dressmaker is the person driving the van##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is the dressmaker##1
7. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
8. the mechanic is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | coach | mechanic | dressmaker | entrepreneur |
| Sport       | parkour     | golf      | climbing     | baseball      |
| Transport   | snowmobile | airplane         | van      | boat        |

