.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, dancing, traveling, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, zombie, musical, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, cricket, baseball
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | traveling   | skydiving | dancing  | sudoku      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | comedy        | family  | zombie       |
| Sport         | basketball | cricket    | cycling | baseball |

