.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, police-officer, analyst, lawyer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, superhero, romance, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, salsa, ambient, dubstep
1. the bartender is the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the lawyer##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
5. the police-officer is on the far left##1
6. the person watching romance movies is the analyst##1
7. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
8. the lawyer is the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | police-officer | analyst | lawyer | bartender |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | romance  | superhero | comedy   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | hip-hop     | ambient | salsa       |

