.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, apricot, mango, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, reading, puzzles, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, sports, horror, documentary
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person watching sports movies is the person eating mango##1
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person eating pear##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the person who's hobby is reading is the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | pear  | strawberry | mango   | apricot     |
| Hobby         | singing | reading   | sudoku  | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | horror         | comedy  | sports | documentary  |

