.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, horror, superhero, musical
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian, colombian, indonesian
1. the person drinking sprite is the colombian##1
2. the indonesian is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the indonesian is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the egyptian is on the left of the indonesian##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | hot-chocolate     | 7up | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | martial-arts | superhero       | horror    |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | indonesian | mexican    | colombian |

