.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, pineapple, lettuce, spinach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, dubstep, techno, folk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of techno##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is the person eating pineapple##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the fan of folk##1
6. the fan of folk is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | lettuce        | spinach   | pineapple  | kale   |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | folk     | dubstep    | techno       |
| Sport         | sailing | skiing | surfing | tennis |

