.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, cola, tea
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, kale, corn, mango
4 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, frog, ferret
1. the person drinking tea is the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating kale##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
5. the person eating corn is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
7. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | cola | tea | hot-chocolate        |
| Food       | mango | cranberry  | kale | corn     |
| Pet        | bird    | frog   | ferret  | hamster |

