.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, analyst, doctor, coach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, badminton, biathlon, golf
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, bike, ship, taxi
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the coach##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the ship##1
8. the person who's sport is biathlon is the fisherman##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | fisherman  | coach | analyst  | doctor |
| Sport       | biathlon | badminton        | golf | parkour       |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | bike          | taxi          | ship       |

