2. the person watching family movies is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the dutch is on the left of the australian##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the british##1
7. the dutch is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | sudoku   | drawing   | woodworking | filmmaking |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | romance | horror   | family |
| Nationality   | dutch     | australian  | british  | egyptian  |

