.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, magic-tricks, photography, reggae-climbing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, funk, reggae, classical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon, rowing, handball
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the fan of classical##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is the fan of classical##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the fan of funk##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the fan of soul##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | reggae-climbing | magic-tricks    | video-games        | photography |
| Music-Genre   | funk     | reggae     | classical        | soul   |
| Sport         | biathlon   | swimming | rowing | handball  |

