.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, documentary, time-travel, action
There are 4 different nationalities: german, malaysian, australian, french
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, ship, quad-bike
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the australian##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the french##1
3. the german is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
8. the malaysian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary   | action  | thriller    | time-travel    |
| Nationality   | french | australian  | german  | malaysian |
| Transport     | quad-bike  | subway | ship | snowmobile        |

