.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, juice, almond-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, satire, zombie, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, basketball, tennis, swimming
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching drama movies##1
8. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate        | almond-milk    | 7up | juice      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama        | scientific   | satire  | zombie  |
| Sport         | swimming | basketball | tennis   | snowboarding |

