4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish | italian | pakistani | japanese |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | soccer  | skiing  |
| Transport     | trike  | taxi | skateboard     | airplane  |

