4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the scientist##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the teacher##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
