.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, coach, pilot, photographer
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, polish, american, australian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, swimming, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the coach is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
4. the american is on the far right##1
5. the turkish is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the australian is on the far left##1
7. the photographer is on the far right##1
8. the australian is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | coach  | pilot  | designer | photographer |
| Nationality   | australian   | turkish | polish   | american      |
| Sport         | handball | water-polo    | swimming   | weightlifting         |

 